[ShankhaNidhi
House](https://bn.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%A6%B6%E0%A6%99%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%96%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%A7%E0%A6%BF_%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%89%E0%A6%9C)।
This is another century-old building in Dhaka. Without preservation, this
building is barely surviving. Image by Shakil Ahmed. Used with permission.

